properties.verseOrder: v1 v2 v3 c1 v4 v5

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Atiyo ne Yesu atiyo ne ngima
aleluya atiyo ne ngima,
atiyo ne Yesu.
Atiyo ne ngima, aleluya
atiyo ne ngima. x2

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Awuothe ne Yesu,
awuothe ne Yesu.
Aleluya awuothe ne ngima,
awuothe ne Yesu.
Awuothe ne ngima,
aleluya awuothe ne ngima.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Abayo ne Yesu
abayo ne ngima.
Aleluya abayo ne ngima,
abayo ne Yesu.
Abayo ne ngima, aleluya
abayo ne ngima. x2

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
Anyuola na duto,
noringo-weya.
Aleluya noringo-weya,
aleluya noringo-weya.
Anyuola na duto noringo-weya.

verse.name: v4
verse.lines:
Owete na duto noringo-weya,
aleluya noringo-weya.
Owetens duto noringo-weya,
aleluya noringo huella.

verse.name: v5
verse.lines:
Adong’gi Yesu adong gi ngima,
Aleluya adong’gi ngima
Adong’gi Yesu, adong’gi ngima.
